1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 16]

2
00:00:16,502 --> 00:00:17,461
That day,

3
00:00:19,582 --> 00:00:20,341
I was poisoned

4
00:00:20,342 --> 00:00:22,301
by Third Concubine's love potion.

5
00:00:23,822 --> 00:00:25,581
I could barely speak,

6
00:00:25,742 --> 00:00:27,341
unable to explain to you

7
00:00:27,542 --> 00:00:29,301
that the ancestral hall incident

8
00:00:29,822 --> 00:00:31,781
was entirely orchestrated by her.

9
00:00:31,902 --> 00:00:33,661
She wanted to get rid of me

10
00:00:33,902 --> 00:00:35,381
because I stood in the way of her plans.

11
00:00:35,382 --> 00:00:36,381
Nonsense!

12
00:00:36,902 --> 00:00:38,221
What plan could I have?

13
00:00:38,222 --> 00:00:39,381
Explain yourself!

14
00:00:39,542 --> 00:00:40,621
What's her plan?

15
00:00:41,062 --> 00:00:42,461
You wouldn't believe it - she pretends to

16
00:00:42,622 --> 00:00:44,981
chant sutras at the Buddhist hall every day,

17
00:00:45,582 --> 00:00:46,621
but really, she's

18
00:00:46,902 --> 00:00:49,301
sneaking off to watch operas next door.

19
00:00:49,382 --> 00:00:50,261
Lies!

20
00:00:50,382 --> 00:00:51,341
Look, Master,

21
00:00:51,462 --> 00:00:52,821
as early as on An He's return day,

22
00:00:52,942 --> 00:00:55,021
I saw Third Concubine at the theater.

23
00:00:55,302 --> 00:00:56,941
Claiming she'd quit opera long ago,

24
00:00:57,462 --> 00:00:58,581
yet secretly,

25
00:00:58,782 --> 00:01:00,541
she's more reckless than Zhou Yimo.

26
00:01:03,102 --> 00:01:05,981
You pawned several Zhou family properties

27
00:01:06,382 --> 00:01:09,021
and eastern farmlands.

28
00:01:09,542 --> 00:01:11,701
After all the trust I placed in you,

29
00:01:12,102 --> 00:01:14,781
entrusting family affairs to your care.

30
00:01:15,662 --> 00:01:17,261
All these years,

31
00:01:17,382 --> 00:01:18,101
you

32
00:01:18,902 --> 00:01:21,621
played me for a fool!

33
00:01:22,622 --> 00:01:24,101
Master! Master!

34
00:01:25,662 --> 00:01:26,501
Third Concubine has

35
00:01:26,502 --> 00:01:28,021
sold many Zhou family assets,

36
00:01:28,382 --> 00:01:29,981
buying a mansion for an actor.

37
00:01:29,982 --> 00:01:32,101
Now without Zhou Yichen covering for you,

38
00:01:32,102 --> 00:01:33,581
aren't you panicking?

39
00:01:33,582 --> 00:01:34,741
Master! Master!

40
00:01:34,742 --> 00:01:35,541
I was wrong!

41
00:01:35,542 --> 00:01:36,341
You schemed relentlessly

42
00:01:36,342 --> 00:01:37,781
to frame me and Zhou Yimo,

43
00:01:37,782 --> 00:01:39,101
trying to eliminate us,

44
00:01:39,542 --> 00:01:40,101
fearing

45
00:01:40,342 --> 00:01:41,581
we might someday

46
00:01:41,582 --> 00:01:42,781
investigate these

47
00:01:42,782 --> 00:01:44,861
messy accounts that only Zhou Yichen knew.

48
00:01:45,222 --> 00:01:45,821
Master,

49
00:01:46,782 --> 00:01:48,261
do you see now?

50
00:01:48,582 --> 00:01:50,141
Zhou Yimo and I are innocent.

51
00:01:50,382 --> 00:01:52,181
Our loyalty is to you.

52
00:01:54,502 --> 00:01:55,141
She

53
00:01:55,582 --> 00:01:56,901
is the true betrayer!

54
00:01:56,902 --> 00:01:58,221
Shut up!

55
00:01:58,542 --> 00:01:59,421
Ye Zhiqiu!

56
00:01:59,582 --> 00:02:00,861
If not for you,

57
00:02:01,502 --> 00:02:03,821
Chen and I would be living well!

58
00:02:03,822 --> 00:02:04,861
Enough!

59
00:02:04,982 --> 00:02:05,901
Hansheng!

60
00:02:06,702 --> 00:02:07,621
Hansheng!

61
00:02:08,582 --> 00:02:09,661
Hansheng!

62
00:02:11,862 --> 00:02:13,141
Take her away!

63
00:02:13,742 --> 00:02:15,581
I don't want to see her again!

64
00:02:15,902 --> 00:02:16,861
Come, Third Concubine.

65
00:02:16,862 --> 00:02:17,901
Don't touch me.

66
00:02:19,862 --> 00:02:21,221
I'll walk myself.

67
00:02:26,862 --> 00:02:27,901
Zhou Huaiqian!

68
00:02:29,462 --> 00:02:31,221
You have five concubines,

69
00:02:32,142 --> 00:02:34,661
why can't I keep one man?

70
00:02:35,422 --> 00:02:36,381
You!

71
00:02:48,742 --> 00:02:49,501
Hansheng!

72
00:02:51,142 --> 00:02:52,661
Get rid of her.

73
00:02:52,982 --> 00:02:54,341
Get rid of her!

74
00:02:54,342 --> 00:02:55,261
Fine!

75
00:02:56,502 --> 00:02:58,421
How should I die?

76
00:02:59,342 --> 00:03:01,341
To be shot like Chen,

77
00:03:01,342 --> 00:03:03,581
or to hang like Fifth Concubine?

78
00:03:04,862 --> 00:03:05,981
My son

79
00:03:06,662 --> 00:03:08,541
did so much for you,

80
00:03:08,902 --> 00:03:10,301
was used by you,

81
00:03:10,302 --> 00:03:11,581
took the blame for you,

82
00:03:13,302 --> 00:03:15,741
never betrayed you even unto death.

83
00:03:16,982 --> 00:03:17,741
And you?

84
00:03:18,982 --> 00:03:20,581
Have you ever shown us

85
00:03:21,382 --> 00:03:23,541
an ounce of mercy?

86
00:03:31,982 --> 00:03:32,781
Master,

87
00:03:33,502 --> 00:03:34,581
this concerns human lives.

88
00:03:35,862 --> 00:03:36,901
Don't act rashly.

89
00:03:39,182 --> 00:03:40,141
Perhaps,

90
00:03:40,262 --> 00:03:41,501
we should confine Third Concubine

91
00:03:41,502 --> 00:03:42,661
to the cold courtyard

92
00:03:43,662 --> 00:03:44,861
and decide later.

93
00:03:59,222 --> 00:04:00,101
Hansheng,

94
00:04:00,622 --> 00:04:02,501
find that opera singer

95
00:04:04,022 --> 00:04:05,861
and eliminate him for me.

96
00:04:06,382 --> 00:04:07,381
Yes, Master.

97
00:04:07,502 --> 00:04:08,221
Also

98
00:04:08,422 --> 00:04:10,821
release Yimo.

99
00:04:11,142 --> 00:04:13,141
He hasn't eaten for three days.

100
00:04:13,302 --> 00:04:13,941
Quickly.

101
00:04:14,382 --> 00:04:15,381
Fifth Concubine,

102
00:04:16,342 --> 00:04:17,261
I'm sorry

103
00:04:17,742 --> 00:04:19,381
for making you suffer this injustice.

104
00:04:19,862 --> 00:04:20,941
As long as you

105
00:04:21,942 --> 00:04:23,101
don't send me away.

106
00:04:24,342 --> 00:04:25,981
This bit of unfairness is nothing.

107
00:04:36,942 --> 00:04:37,581
Master

108
00:04:38,902 --> 00:04:40,581
you must take care of your health.

109
00:04:51,782 --> 00:04:53,901
♪ Resting in the underworld, ♪

110
00:04:54,182 --> 00:04:56,101
♪ dreams elude me. ♪

111
00:04:57,022 --> 00:04:59,181
♪ In this life I've accumulated ♪

112
00:04:59,382 --> 00:05:01,941
♪ so many affections. ♪

113
00:05:02,862 --> 00:05:03,901
♪ Here I am, ♪

114
00:05:03,902 --> 00:05:05,781
♪ drunkenly lying ♪

115
00:05:06,782 --> 00:05:08,181
♪ in the Plum Blossom ♪

116
00:05:08,542 --> 00:05:10,541
♪ Temple courtyard. ♪

117
00:05:10,542 --> 00:05:11,821
Do you remember

118
00:05:12,582 --> 00:05:13,901
the owner of these clothes?

119
00:05:16,822 --> 00:05:18,701
♪ Hearing loud shouts ♪

120
00:05:18,782 --> 00:05:20,021
♪ from inside. ♪

121
00:05:20,422 --> 00:05:22,141
That opera singer is way too delicate.

122
00:05:22,182 --> 00:05:23,101
He can't take a beating.

123
00:05:24,022 --> 00:05:25,021
After just a few strikes,

124
00:05:25,702 --> 00:05:26,901
he confessed everything.

125
00:05:28,782 --> 00:05:30,381
They took every secret meeting you had,

126
00:05:30,542 --> 00:05:32,461
and all the gold and silver

127
00:05:32,982 --> 00:05:34,221
you gave him, as evidence.

128
00:05:37,982 --> 00:05:38,901
Ye Zhiqiu!

129
00:05:38,902 --> 00:05:39,981
Why did you have to

130
00:05:39,982 --> 00:05:41,301
treat my son and me this way?

131
00:05:41,302 --> 00:05:42,941
How have we wronged you?

132
00:05:44,462 --> 00:05:45,581
Even now

133
00:05:45,582 --> 00:05:47,461
you still claim innocence?

134
00:05:49,422 --> 00:05:51,621
If you hadn't seduced Chen,

135
00:05:52,182 --> 00:05:53,741
exposing everything,

136
00:05:54,542 --> 00:05:56,501
he wouldn't have died.

137
00:05:56,862 --> 00:05:57,581
So anyone

138
00:05:57,582 --> 00:05:59,181
who approaches Zhou Yichen with kindness

139
00:06:00,662 --> 00:06:02,141
must be slandered,

140
00:06:02,662 --> 00:06:03,461
framed by you?

141
00:06:03,942 --> 00:06:04,901
Kindness?

142
00:06:05,742 --> 00:06:06,501
Come,

143
00:06:06,782 --> 00:06:07,781
let me hear

144
00:06:08,182 --> 00:06:09,421
what kindness you have.

145
00:06:11,942 --> 00:06:12,901
I have none.

146
00:06:19,102 --> 00:06:20,101
But someone

147
00:06:21,782 --> 00:06:23,421
once cared for Zhou Yichen

148
00:06:23,422 --> 00:06:25,141
with genuine kindness and compassion.

149
00:06:26,742 --> 00:06:28,781
But you nearly sold her to a brothel.

150
00:06:29,582 --> 00:06:30,901
Do you still remember her?

151
00:06:33,142 --> 00:06:34,341
Chuxue?

152
00:06:36,262 --> 00:06:37,421
How do you know?

153
00:06:37,582 --> 00:06:38,621
That bitch!

154
00:06:38,622 --> 00:06:39,621
Bitch?

155
00:06:40,982 --> 00:06:42,461
All she did was show Zhou Yichen

156
00:06:42,462 --> 00:06:44,861
a little basic human kindness.

157
00:06:47,182 --> 00:06:48,141
She saw you

158
00:06:48,742 --> 00:06:50,661
destroying the sculptures he loved,

159
00:06:50,662 --> 00:06:51,901
so she hid them for him.

160
00:06:52,622 --> 00:06:53,541
She saw you

161
00:06:54,182 --> 00:06:55,021
forcing him

162
00:06:55,222 --> 00:06:56,421
to grovel before the master,

163
00:06:56,422 --> 00:06:57,661
so she offered him comfort.

164
00:06:57,662 --> 00:06:58,701
That was all.

165
00:06:59,022 --> 00:06:59,981
And just for that,

166
00:07:01,182 --> 00:07:03,661
you call her bitch?

167
00:07:05,022 --> 00:07:06,581
Sold an innocent girl

168
00:07:07,542 --> 00:07:08,861
to a brothel?

169
00:07:10,102 --> 00:07:11,581
Luckily for her,

170
00:07:11,582 --> 00:07:12,861
she escaped.

171
00:07:15,182 --> 00:07:15,661
No.

172
00:07:17,182 --> 00:07:18,701
She was rescued

173
00:07:19,502 --> 00:07:20,741
by your precious son!

174
00:07:25,862 --> 00:07:27,021
What are you talking about?

175
00:07:28,982 --> 00:07:30,301
Is Chuxue inside?

176
00:07:30,422 --> 00:07:31,221
Hurry, hurry!

177
00:07:33,022 --> 00:07:33,821
Third...

178
00:07:34,142 --> 00:07:35,501
Third Concubine!

179
00:07:35,622 --> 00:07:37,221
I'm grinding ink for the young master.

180
00:07:37,222 --> 00:07:39,101
Someone outside Zhou residence is asking for you.

181
00:07:39,102 --> 00:07:39,861
Okay.

182
00:07:39,942 --> 00:07:40,781
I'll be right there.

183
00:08:12,222 --> 00:08:13,341
Accept your fate.

184
00:08:13,702 --> 00:08:15,941
Master sold you to the south.

185
00:08:16,782 --> 00:08:17,621
Please,

186
00:08:17,622 --> 00:08:19,181
please let me go!

187
00:08:19,662 --> 00:08:20,901
Please release me!

188
00:08:26,462 --> 00:08:27,261
Second Young Master!

189
00:08:27,302 --> 00:08:27,941
Second Young Master!

190
00:08:28,102 --> 00:08:29,021
The moment I left the residence,

191
00:08:29,022 --> 00:08:30,581
they sold me here!

192
00:08:30,582 --> 00:08:31,341
I know.

193
00:08:31,382 --> 00:08:31,941
I know.

194
00:08:31,942 --> 00:08:32,781
I know everything.

195
00:08:33,582 --> 00:08:34,501
After returning,

196
00:08:34,902 --> 00:08:36,501
don't mention this to anyone.

197
00:08:36,702 --> 00:08:37,541
I'll arrange for you

198
00:08:37,542 --> 00:08:38,861
to work for Second Concubine.

199
00:08:39,502 --> 00:08:40,261
But...

200
00:08:40,862 --> 00:08:41,581
we must keep

201
00:08:41,582 --> 00:08:42,941
some distance between us.

202
00:08:46,022 --> 00:08:46,901
Why?

203
00:08:48,102 --> 00:08:48,781
Did...

204
00:08:48,942 --> 00:08:50,581
Did I do something wrong?

205
00:08:51,422 --> 00:08:52,901
I'll double your salary.

206
00:08:53,662 --> 00:08:54,461
But...

207
00:08:56,782 --> 00:08:58,341
you can't stay by my side anymore.

208
00:09:13,382 --> 00:09:15,661
To protect Chuxue from your persecution,

209
00:09:16,262 --> 00:09:17,941
Zhou Yichen had to hand her

210
00:09:17,942 --> 00:09:19,261
over to Second Concubine.

211
00:09:20,222 --> 00:09:21,621
He watched her endure humiliation

212
00:09:22,942 --> 00:09:24,581
but dared not intervene again.

213
00:09:28,862 --> 00:09:30,581
My son is too kindhearted.

214
00:09:31,102 --> 00:09:32,301
To sacrifice so much for

215
00:09:32,302 --> 00:09:33,941
such a worthless, lowly creature...

216
00:09:36,582 --> 00:09:38,021
In her family's eyes,

217
00:09:39,342 --> 00:09:39,981
you're nothing

218
00:09:39,982 --> 00:09:41,981
but a useless piece of trash.

219
00:09:47,342 --> 00:09:49,221
What's your connection to Chuxue?

220
00:09:50,222 --> 00:09:51,181
How do you know so much

221
00:09:51,182 --> 00:09:52,221
about her?

222
00:09:53,142 --> 00:09:54,901
Why did you marry into this family?

223
00:09:56,462 --> 00:09:57,781
I spared your life

224
00:09:58,702 --> 00:09:59,621
only out of respect

225
00:09:59,622 --> 00:10:01,301
for your past with Zhou Yichen.

226
00:10:03,382 --> 00:10:04,581
From now on,

227
00:10:06,582 --> 00:10:08,821
you'll never rise again.

228
00:10:20,902 --> 00:10:22,101
Ye Zhiqiu,

229
00:10:22,102 --> 00:10:23,701
you'll meet a bad end!

230
00:10:26,222 --> 00:10:27,701
People in the Zhou family

231
00:10:28,662 --> 00:10:30,741
never come to a good end.

232
00:10:32,342 --> 00:10:33,581
You're no exception.

233
00:11:02,262 --> 00:11:02,901
Sister,

234
00:11:03,342 --> 00:11:04,261
are you watching?

235
00:11:04,822 --> 00:11:06,341
I'll make every

236
00:11:06,582 --> 00:11:07,901
single one who bullied you

237
00:11:08,142 --> 00:11:09,981
pay the price.

238
00:11:10,382 --> 00:11:11,621
Extra, extra!

239
00:11:11,662 --> 00:11:12,701
Last copy available!

240
00:11:12,822 --> 00:11:13,741
Fifth Concubine of the Zhou family

241
00:11:13,782 --> 00:11:15,581
and eldest son are siblings!

242
00:11:15,582 --> 00:11:16,301
One copy, please!

243
00:11:19,502 --> 00:11:20,341
Give me one!

244
00:11:25,862 --> 00:11:27,261
The papers are selling well today.

245
00:11:27,262 --> 00:11:28,101
Today's news

246
00:11:28,102 --> 00:11:29,421
is worth every penny!

247
00:11:29,542 --> 00:11:30,661
Bizarre twists and turns

248
00:11:30,662 --> 00:11:31,581
happened right in

249
00:11:31,582 --> 00:11:33,301
the wealthiest family in Wu County!

250
00:11:33,502 --> 00:11:34,581
It says here

251
00:11:34,582 --> 00:11:35,341
the Fifth Concubine

252
00:11:35,342 --> 00:11:36,901
was framed by the other concubines.

253
00:11:37,022 --> 00:11:37,861
Is that true?

254
00:11:37,942 --> 00:11:38,501
Of course!

255
00:11:38,502 --> 00:11:39,461
Once Master He intervened,

256
00:11:39,462 --> 00:11:40,941
the truth came to light.

257
00:11:41,022 --> 00:11:41,861
The fallen heiress

258
00:11:41,862 --> 00:11:43,341
and the wealthy heir are siblings.

259
00:11:43,342 --> 00:11:44,501
How could they be lovers?

260
00:11:44,502 --> 00:11:45,501
Someone must have

261
00:11:45,502 --> 00:11:46,981
bullied her behind the scenes.

262
00:11:47,582 --> 00:11:48,701
So that means

263
00:11:48,702 --> 00:11:49,661
crossing her

264
00:11:49,662 --> 00:11:50,781
means crossing

265
00:11:50,782 --> 00:11:52,261
that mysterious He family big shot?

266
00:11:52,262 --> 00:11:53,461
Naturally.

267
00:11:53,662 --> 00:11:54,781
That He family big shot

268
00:11:54,782 --> 00:11:56,341
holds immense power, they say.

269
00:11:58,502 --> 00:11:59,101
Alright.

270
00:11:59,222 --> 00:11:59,781
Let me see.

271
00:11:59,782 --> 00:12:00,461
Here.

272
00:12:01,582 --> 00:12:02,221
Take it.

273
00:12:03,222 --> 00:12:03,901
What's wrong?

274
00:12:04,142 --> 00:12:05,101
What do you mean?

275
00:12:05,302 --> 00:12:05,861
Look.

276
00:12:05,862 --> 00:12:06,981
Extra, extra!

277
00:12:06,982 --> 00:12:07,781
We made

278
00:12:07,782 --> 00:12:09,621
the front page headline in Wu County today!

279
00:12:10,982 --> 00:12:12,461
Just some bored reporters

280
00:12:12,462 --> 00:12:14,141
writing sensational stories.

281
00:12:14,222 --> 00:12:15,221
Boring news.

282
00:12:15,542 --> 00:12:16,461
And all that nonsense about

283
00:12:16,462 --> 00:12:17,581
a fallen heiress

284
00:12:17,582 --> 00:12:19,581
and a wealthy heir being siblings.

285
00:12:19,702 --> 00:12:20,861
The generations are all mixed up.

286
00:12:21,662 --> 00:12:22,101
I played the role

287
00:12:22,102 --> 00:12:22,541
of your brother

288
00:12:22,542 --> 00:12:23,221
and your father.

289
00:12:23,222 --> 00:12:24,141
What are you afraid of?

290
00:12:26,542 --> 00:12:27,621
Unless

291
00:12:27,622 --> 00:12:28,901
you want to be something else to me?

292
00:12:28,902 --> 00:12:29,741
Shut up!

293
00:12:30,542 --> 00:12:32,421
Tomorrow I'll warn the newspaper office.

294
00:12:32,462 --> 00:12:33,221
If they keep writing nonsense...

295
00:12:33,222 --> 00:12:33,861
No, no.

296
00:12:34,502 --> 00:12:35,501
I'll have them

297
00:12:35,742 --> 00:12:37,341
print a corrected version tomorrow.

298
00:12:40,462 --> 00:12:41,261
Zhou Yimo!

299
00:12:42,022 --> 00:12:42,941
What do you mean?

300
00:12:45,302 --> 00:12:47,541
The entire publishing industry is mine.

301
00:12:47,622 --> 00:12:48,781
What do you think I mean?

302
00:12:50,742 --> 00:12:52,021
So these articles

303
00:12:52,342 --> 00:12:53,821
were arranged by you?

304
00:12:54,782 --> 00:12:55,981
Why would you do this?

305
00:12:57,182 --> 00:12:57,941
Using sensational stories

306
00:12:57,942 --> 00:12:59,461
to obscure our relationship?

307
00:13:00,462 --> 00:13:01,461
But it's unnecessary.

308
00:13:01,462 --> 00:13:02,141
I don't need it.

309
00:13:02,142 --> 00:13:03,181
I say you do.

310
00:13:08,462 --> 00:13:10,021
You're just pretending not to care.

311
00:13:11,702 --> 00:13:12,981
But every day I see

312
00:13:12,982 --> 00:13:13,861
them misunderstanding you,

313
00:13:13,982 --> 00:13:14,581
slandering you,

314
00:13:14,582 --> 00:13:15,421
looking down on you.

315
00:13:15,582 --> 00:13:17,021
I want every newspaper's

316
00:13:17,022 --> 00:13:19,141
front page to proclaim your innocence.

317
00:13:28,222 --> 00:13:29,221
There are a lot of people around.

318
00:13:41,622 --> 00:13:42,381
Is this

319
00:13:43,182 --> 00:13:44,141
okay?

320
00:14:08,342 --> 00:14:09,541
Any new leads?

321
00:14:10,182 --> 00:14:10,981
I secretly checked

322
00:14:10,982 --> 00:14:12,221
the housekeeper's records.

323
00:14:13,102 --> 00:14:14,501
On New Year's Eve three years ago,

324
00:14:14,502 --> 00:14:15,781
all the servants were together

325
00:14:16,022 --> 00:14:17,381
with mutual alibis.

326
00:14:18,222 --> 00:14:18,901
Besides,

327
00:14:19,382 --> 00:14:20,741
they didn't have the freedom

328
00:14:20,742 --> 00:14:22,541
to move around the mansion unnoticed.

329
00:14:22,702 --> 00:14:24,101
Could it be the Third Concubine?

330
00:14:24,302 --> 00:14:25,381
The Third Concubine is suspicious.

331
00:14:25,862 --> 00:14:27,301
But Nanxi told me

332
00:14:27,782 --> 00:14:28,941
that on New Year's Eve,

333
00:14:28,942 --> 00:14:30,101
she accompanied the Third Concubine

334
00:14:30,262 --> 00:14:31,821
chanting scriptures in the hall until dawn.

335
00:14:33,102 --> 00:14:33,901
Moreover,

336
00:14:34,102 --> 00:14:35,341
this was also corroborated

337
00:14:35,342 --> 00:14:36,741
by the housekeeper and driver.

338
00:14:37,182 --> 00:14:38,181
It's just a pity I wasn't

339
00:14:38,182 --> 00:14:40,101
at the mansion that New Year's Eve.

340
00:14:40,582 --> 00:14:42,181
But Nanxi's account seems reliable.

341
00:14:42,622 --> 00:14:43,581
There's another person

342
00:14:43,862 --> 00:14:45,581
who left in a hurry

343
00:14:45,782 --> 00:14:47,141
after the reunion dinner.

344
00:14:47,582 --> 00:14:48,261
Who?

345
00:14:48,462 --> 00:14:49,381
The Fourth Concubine.

346
00:14:49,822 --> 00:14:50,981
But investigating her

347
00:14:51,262 --> 00:14:51,981
is difficult.

348
00:14:53,262 --> 00:14:54,901
She hasn't returned for three years.

349
00:15:00,942 --> 00:15:01,541
Young Master,

350
00:15:01,902 --> 00:15:02,581
Fifth Concubine,

351
00:15:02,902 --> 00:15:03,901
the Master is critically ill.

352
00:15:04,302 --> 00:15:05,221
Perhaps

353
00:15:05,782 --> 00:15:07,781
you'll see the Fourth Concubine soon.

354
00:15:12,982 --> 00:15:14,301
Father, rest assured.

355
00:15:14,862 --> 00:15:16,621
I will manage

356
00:15:16,622 --> 00:15:17,861
the Zhou family's business

357
00:15:17,862 --> 00:15:19,421
diligently for you.

358
00:15:24,702 --> 00:15:25,301
Here,

359
00:15:25,822 --> 00:15:27,221
let's add a thumbprint.

360
00:15:34,382 --> 00:15:34,981
Master Zhou,

361
00:15:34,982 --> 00:15:35,781
as per your instructions,

362
00:15:35,782 --> 00:15:36,901
all Zhou family assets

363
00:15:36,902 --> 00:15:37,861
in Wu County

364
00:15:37,862 --> 00:15:38,701
have been transferred

365
00:15:38,742 --> 00:15:40,381
to your eldest son, Zhou Yimo.

366
00:15:40,702 --> 00:15:42,421
But properties outside Wu County

367
00:15:42,422 --> 00:15:43,861
remain under Fourth Concubine's control.

368
00:15:43,862 --> 00:15:44,861
After her return,

369
00:15:44,862 --> 00:15:45,981
we'll make further decisions.

370
00:15:45,982 --> 00:15:46,781
Dismissed.

371
00:15:47,302 --> 00:15:48,901
I'd like a private word with Father.

372
00:15:49,582 --> 00:15:49,981
Go.

373
00:15:57,462 --> 00:15:58,261
Dad,

374
00:15:59,102 --> 00:16:00,821
why are you so insistent on passing

375
00:16:00,822 --> 00:16:01,701
our family business to me?

376
00:16:02,702 --> 00:16:04,701
Fourth Concubine has been working hard,

377
00:16:04,702 --> 00:16:05,901
raising two children.

378
00:16:06,102 --> 00:16:07,101
It hasn't been easy for her.

379
00:16:07,302 --> 00:16:08,221
Mo,

380
00:16:09,662 --> 00:16:10,861
take it back!

381
00:16:13,582 --> 00:16:14,461
Why?

382
00:16:17,462 --> 00:16:18,701
It's all mine!

383
00:16:20,222 --> 00:16:21,501
Why should I give it to her?

384
00:16:21,502 --> 00:16:22,581
It's all yours.

385
00:16:24,942 --> 00:16:26,861
She has done so much for the family.

386
00:16:27,462 --> 00:16:28,461
Does none of that count?

387
00:16:29,462 --> 00:16:30,581
It doesn't.

388
00:16:32,502 --> 00:16:33,941
Nobody

389
00:16:35,462 --> 00:16:36,661
is

390
00:16:36,662 --> 00:16:37,581
taking

391
00:16:37,582 --> 00:16:39,141
what's mine.

392
00:16:44,222 --> 00:16:44,861
Dad,

393
00:16:45,422 --> 00:16:47,341
you've always only cared about yourself.

394
00:16:47,862 --> 00:16:49,261
Starting with my mother.

395
00:16:49,582 --> 00:16:50,661
You married her

396
00:16:50,742 --> 00:16:52,661
just to get the He family's wealth.

397
00:16:52,862 --> 00:16:54,341
You think I didn't know?

398
00:16:54,742 --> 00:16:55,901
Back then, you knew Second Concubine

399
00:16:55,902 --> 00:16:56,981
was going to set fire to kill my mother,

400
00:16:56,982 --> 00:16:58,301
yet you let it happen.

401
00:17:00,742 --> 00:17:01,341
You...

402
00:17:02,142 --> 00:17:03,581
You knew?

403
00:17:05,662 --> 00:17:06,461
Dad,

404
00:17:06,462 --> 00:17:08,381
come save my mother!

405
00:17:09,662 --> 00:17:11,381
It was all your terrible idea.

406
00:17:11,542 --> 00:17:13,461
You actually had them burned to death.

407
00:17:13,982 --> 00:17:14,941
What's there to fear?

408
00:17:15,582 --> 00:17:17,661
Zhou Yimo isn't even your real son anyway.

409
00:17:18,702 --> 00:17:19,581
Later,

410
00:17:21,462 --> 00:17:22,661
I'll have as many kids

411
00:17:25,662 --> 00:17:26,581
as you want for you.

412
00:17:28,942 --> 00:17:29,581
Good.

413
00:17:30,182 --> 00:17:31,581
Bear me several more, okay?

414
00:17:32,542 --> 00:17:34,021
I grew up filled with hatred,

415
00:17:34,582 --> 00:17:35,541
only to discover that you turned

416
00:17:35,542 --> 00:17:37,421
the He family's thriving tea business

417
00:17:37,422 --> 00:17:39,541
into a cover for your opium smuggling.

418
00:17:39,542 --> 00:17:40,381
I've always known about

419
00:17:40,382 --> 00:17:41,781
the schemes you and Yichen were pulling.

420
00:17:42,502 --> 00:17:44,301
All these years I've been biding my time,

421
00:17:44,582 --> 00:17:46,661
gathering the He family's influence.

422
00:17:46,662 --> 00:17:47,941
All so that one day,

423
00:17:47,942 --> 00:17:48,821
I could take revenge for my mother

424
00:17:48,822 --> 00:17:50,661
and reclaim the He family's legacy.

425
00:17:59,982 --> 00:18:01,021
You still don't know,

426
00:18:03,022 --> 00:18:04,701
that Master He you've been searching for

427
00:18:05,702 --> 00:18:06,581
is me.

428
00:18:07,662 --> 00:18:08,501
Also,

429
00:18:10,982 --> 00:18:11,901
I like

430
00:18:12,902 --> 00:18:14,141
Fifth Concubine very much.

431
00:18:16,382 --> 00:18:18,501
I'll take good care of her for you.
